This example shows the support of the IÂ²C driver for the Wemos SSD1306 oled display
controller, it is a 64 x 48 Oled display board.
For Wemos Oled you need to connect the reset pin D3, for this example it is connected 
to the GPIO_0_0 of the micro-controller.
The other pins are:
D1 -> SCL
D2 -> SDA
GND 
3V3 
